8 SUMMARY
169 This bill adds renovating school kitchens and cafeterias and replacing or adding kitchen
1170 equipment to facilitate the serving of meals to students to the purposes of the School
1181 Revolving Renovation Fund. The bill also removes from the School Meal Equipment and
1192 Program Improvement Fund reimbursement for food costs related to medically necessary
2103 dietary restrictions of students from the approved uses of grants provided by that fund. The
2114 bill also provides appropriations and allocations to the School Meal Equipment and
2125 Program Improvement Fund.
